Select Next (Cmd-D) does't match partial words. Selecting fruit on line 1 then pressing Cmd-D does not select fruit on line 2 as you would expect. I end up having to manually edit because I can't select all the occurrences I need.

Find Next (Cmd-G) is able to match partial words which seems inconsistent with Select Next. Selecting fruit on line 1 then pressing Cmd-F (to put it in search buffer), then Cmd-G does select fruit on line 2.
